thread.title: Max
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Max

author: Max
title: Max
text: The service received at the front desk was brilliant. Quick, easy, professional, however the car itself was a little lacklustre. Totally functional car and no issues with the performance, but when I booked a premium car I expected it to be a little more modern (I.e car radio did not have bluetooth). Would use again though and would recommend to family and friends.
